  api/
  cli/
```

## Local provider examples

Ollama:

```bash
agent-manager --provider ollama --model llama3.1 "Summarize this repository."
```

vLLM:

```bash
agent-manager --provider vllm --model NousResearch/Meta-Llama-3-8B-Instruct "Summarize this repository."
```
